LanguageData.ColonistsBittenByZombieDesc:
These colonists have been bitten by a zombie. At this point, it is unclear whether they will develop an infection:

{0}
Monitor their wounds closely because infections take some time to develop.

LanguageData.ImminentZombiInfectionDesc:
These colonists are about to be infected from a zombie bite:

{0}
You may rescue them by immediately giving them optimal treatment under the best conditions. This requires a good doctor, a quality medical bed, a sterile room, and a vitals monitor.

LanguageData.ZombieInfectionDesc:
These colonists have been infected and will become zombies. There is no way to rescue them anymore:

{0}
During their infection they are indifferent to thoughts, feelings, pain, and hunger. At the end, they die and become zombies.
